==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[How]] [[are]] [[you]]?'''

# {{idiom}} An informal greeting, not requiring a literal response.  Typical responses include:
#: ''I'm very well, thank you. How are you?'' (formal)
#: ''I'm fine, thank you.''
#: ''Fine, thanks.'' (informal)

====Usage note====
For some languages a difference is made between polite and casual forms.

